<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta
      name="viewport"
      content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no"
    />

    <!-- Custom Fonts -->
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Roboto&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />

    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.0/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      integrity="sha384-9aIt2nRpC12Uk9gS9baDl411NQApFmC26EwAOH8WgZl5MYYxFfc+NcPb1dKGj7Sk"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />

    <!-- Custom CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/custom.css" />

    <title>Michael Chladon</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('layout/navbar'); -%>

    <div class="jumbotron jumbotron-fluid">
      <div class="container text-center">
        <h1 class="emph-font">songtrace</h1>
        <h4 class="emph-font">Personal Project</h4>
        <h5 class="emph-font">Summer 2020</h5>
        <p>
          Independently conceived and developed a proof-of-concept web
          application designed to document and visualize memories associated
          with songs
        </p>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col">
            <a href="https://songtrace.herokuapp.com/" target="_blank">
              <button class="btn btn-primary emph-font">View App</button>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="songtrace-carousel-wrapper" class="container">
          <div
            id="songtrace-carousel"
            class="carousel slide"
            data-ride="carousel"
          >
            <ol class="carousel-indicators">
              <li
                data-target="#songtrace-carousel"
                data-slide-to="0"
                class="active"
              ></li>
              <li data-target="#songtrace-carousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
              <li data-target="#songtrace-carousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
              <li data-target="#songtrace-carousel" data-slide-to="3"></li>
            </ol>
            <div class="carousel-inner">
              <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img
                  class="d-block w-100"
                  src="/img/projects/songtrace/st-home.png"
                  alt="songtrace Home Page"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img
                  class="d-block w-100"
                  src="/img/projects/songtrace/st-song.png"
                  alt="songtrace Song Page"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img
                  class="d-block w-100"
                  src="/img/projects/songtrace/st-timeline.png"
                  alt="songtrace Timeline Page"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img
                  class="d-block w-100"
                  src="/img/projects/songtrace/st-map.png"
                  alt="songtrace Map Page"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
            <a
              class="carousel-control-prev"
              href="#songtrace-carousel"
              role="button"
              data-slide="prev"
            >
              <span
                class="carousel-control-prev-icon"
                aria-hidden="true"
              ></span>
              <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
            </a>
            <a
              class="carousel-control-next"
              href="#songtrace-carousel"
              role="button"
              data-slide="next"
            >
              <span
                class="carousel-control-next-icon"
                aria-hidden="true"
              ></span>
              <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="emph-font text-center">Skills Demonstrated</h2>
      <hr />
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <h4 class="emph-font text-center">Front-End</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>HTML</li>
            <li>CSS</li>
            <li>jQuery</li>
            <li>Bootstrap</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <h4 class="emph-font text-center">Back-End</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Node.js</li>
            <li>Express</li>
            <li>MongoDB</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <h4 class="emph-font text-center">Data</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Spotify and MapQuest API Integration</li>
            <li>MongoDB Charts</li>
            <li>MapBox</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <h2 class="emph-font text-center">Overview</h2>
      <hr />
      <p>
        The inspiration for songtrace was to create an interesting way to
        document the memories I associate with the songs in a large playlist
        I've been adding to since my freshman year of college. This vision was
        realized by
        <strong>building a web application using several technologies I had learned
        over the last year.</strong>
      </p>
      <p>
        The current version of the app not only allows a user to record memories
        and store them in a MongoDB database, but also
        <strong>provides extended insights into the data</strong> by integrating
        Spotify and MapQuest
        <strong>APIs and data visualization libraries.</strong>
      </p>
      <p>
        The app is
        <strong>currently deployed for demonstration purposes</strong> using
        Heroku and MongoDB Atlas. A link can be found at the top of this page.
      </p>
    </div>

    <%- include('layout/footer'); -%>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.js"></script>
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.0/dist/umd/popper.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-Q6E9RHvbIyZFJoft+2mJbHaEWldlvI9IOYy5n3zV9zzTtmI3UksdQRVvoxMfooAo"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <script
      src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-OgVRvuATP1z7JjHLkuOU7Xw704+h835Lr+6QL9UvYjZE3Ipu6Tp75j7Bh/kR0JKI"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>
